{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.1","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:1","prev_osis_id":"Acts.014.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Discussion dans l\u2019\u00c9glise d\u2019Antioche relativement \u00e0 l\u2019observation des lois c\u00e9r\u00e9monielles de Mo\u00efse par les pa\u00efens qui embrassent le christianisme. \u2014 Conf\u00e9rence de J\u00e9rusalem<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-12: cf. Ga 2:1-9. Ac 14:27.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Quelques hommes, venus de la Jud\u00e9e, enseignaient les fr\u00e8res, en disant: Si vous n\u2019\u00eates circoncis selon le rite de Mo\u00efse, vous ne pouvez \u00eatre sauv\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.2","name":"Actes 15:2","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.14.28","name":"Actes 14:28","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.14.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.2","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:2","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Paul et Barnabas eurent avec eux un d\u00e9bat et une vive discussion; et les fr\u00e8res d\u00e9cid\u00e8rent que Paul et Barnabas, et quelques-uns des leurs, monteraient \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem vers les ap\u00f4tres et les anciens, pour traiter cette question.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.3","name":"Actes 15:3","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.1","name":"Actes 15:1","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.3","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:3","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s avoir \u00e9t\u00e9 accompagn\u00e9s par l\u2019\u00c9glise, ils poursuivirent leur route \u00e0 travers la Ph\u00e9nicie et la Samarie, racontant la conversion des pa\u00efens, et ils caus\u00e8rent une grande joie \u00e0 tous les fr\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.4","name":"Actes 15:4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.2","name":"Actes 15:2","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.4","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:4","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Arriv\u00e9s \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, ils furent re\u00e7us par l\u2019\u00c9glise, les ap\u00f4tres et les anciens, et ils racont\u00e8rent tout ce que Dieu avait fait avec eux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.5","name":"Actes 15:5","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.3","name":"Actes 15:3","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.5","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:5","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Alors quelques-uns du parti des pharisiens, qui avaient cru, se lev\u00e8rent, en disant qu\u2019il fallait circoncire les pa\u00efens et exiger l\u2019observation de la loi de Mo\u00efse.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.6","name":"Actes 15:6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.4","name":"Actes 15:4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.6","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:6","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Les ap\u00f4tres et les anciens se r\u00e9unirent pour examiner cette affaire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.7","name":"Actes 15:7","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.5","name":"Actes 15:5","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.7","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:7","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Une grande discussion s\u2019\u00e9tant engag\u00e9e, Pierre se leva, et leur dit: Hommes fr\u00e8res, vous savez que d\u00e8s longtemps Dieu a fait un choix parmi vous, afin que, par ma bouche, les pa\u00efens entendissent la parole de l\u2019\u00c9vangile et qu\u2019ils crussent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.8","name":"Actes 15:8","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.6","name":"Actes 15:6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.8","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:8","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Et Dieu, qui conna\u00eet les c\u0153urs, leur a rendu t\u00e9moignage, en leur donnant le Saint-Esprit comme \u00e0 nous;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.9","name":"Actes 15:9","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.7","name":"Actes 15:7","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.9","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:9","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>il n\u2019a fait aucune diff\u00e9rence entre nous et eux, ayant purifi\u00e9 leurs c\u0153urs par la foi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.10","name":"Actes 15:10","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.8","name":"Actes 15:8","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.10","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:10","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Maintenant donc, pourquoi tentez-vous Dieu, en mettant sur le cou des disciples un joug que ni nos p\u00e8res ni nous n\u2019avons pu porter?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.11","name":"Actes 15:11","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.9","name":"Actes 15:9","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.11","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:11","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Mais c\u2019est par la gr\u00e2ce du Seigneur J\u00e9sus que nous croyons \u00eatre sauv\u00e9s, de la m\u00eame mani\u00e8re qu\u2019eux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.12","name":"Actes 15:12","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.10","name":"Actes 15:10","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.12","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:12","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Toute l\u2019assembl\u00e9e garda le silence, et l\u2019on \u00e9couta Barnabas et Paul, qui racont\u00e8rent tous les miracles et les prodiges que Dieu avait faits par eux au milieu des pa\u00efens.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.13","name":"Actes 15:13","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.11","name":"Actes 15:11","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.13","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:13","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.014,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 13-29: cf. Ro 15:8-12. (Col 2:11-17. Ga 5:1-6.) \u00c9s 8:20. Ac 21:25.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019ils eurent cess\u00e9 de parler, Jacques prit la parole, et dit: Hommes fr\u00e8res, \u00e9coutez-moi!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.14","name":"Actes 15:14","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.12","name":"Actes 15:12","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.14","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:14","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Simon a racont\u00e9 comment Dieu a d\u2019abord jet\u00e9 les regards sur les nations pour choisir du milieu d\u2019elles un peuple qui port\u00e2t son nom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.15","name":"Actes 15:15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.13","name":"Actes 15:13","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.15","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:15","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Et avec cela s\u2019accordent les paroles des proph\u00e8tes, selon qu\u2019il est \u00e9crit:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.16","name":"Actes 15:16","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.14","name":"Actes 15:14","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.16","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:16","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>\n    Apr\u00e8s cela, je reviendrai, et je rel\u00e8verai de sa chute la tente de David,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">J\u2019en r\u00e9parerai les ruines, et je la redresserai,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.17","name":"Actes 15:17","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.15","name":"Actes 15:15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.17","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:17","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Afin que le reste des hommes cherche le Seigneur,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ainsi que toutes les nations sur lesquelles mon nom est invoqu\u00e9,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Dit le Seigneur, qui fait ces choses,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.18","name":"Actes 15:18","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.16","name":"Actes 15:16","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.18","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:18","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Et \u00e0 qui elles sont connues de toute \u00e9ternit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.19","name":"Actes 15:19","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.17","name":"Actes 15:17","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.19","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:19","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi je suis d\u2019avis qu\u2019on ne cr\u00e9e pas des difficult\u00e9s \u00e0 ceux des pa\u00efens qui se convertissent \u00e0 Dieu,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.20","name":"Actes 15:20","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.18","name":"Actes 15:18","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.20","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:20","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>mais qu\u2019on leur \u00e9crive de s\u2019abstenir des souillures des idoles, de l\u2019impudicit\u00e9, des animaux \u00e9touff\u00e9s et du sang.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.21","name":"Actes 15:21","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.19","name":"Actes 15:19","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.21","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:21","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Car, depuis bien des g\u00e9n\u00e9rations, Mo\u00efse a dans chaque ville des gens qui le pr\u00eachent, puisqu\u2019on le lit tous les jours de sabbat dans les synagogues.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.22","name":"Actes 15:22","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.20","name":"Actes 15:20","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.22","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:22","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Alors il parut bon aux ap\u00f4tres et aux anciens, et \u00e0 toute l\u2019\u00c9glise, de choisir parmi eux et d\u2019envoyer \u00e0 Antioche, avec Paul et Barnabas, Jude appel\u00e9 Barsabas et Silas, hommes consid\u00e9r\u00e9s entre les fr\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.23","name":"Actes 15:23","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.21","name":"Actes 15:21","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.23","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:23","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Ils les charg\u00e8rent d\u2019une lettre ainsi con\u00e7ue: Les ap\u00f4tres, les anciens, et les fr\u00e8res, aux fr\u00e8res d\u2019entre les pa\u00efens, qui sont \u00e0 Antioche, en Syrie, et en Cilicie, salut!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.24","name":"Actes 15:24","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.22","name":"Actes 15:22","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.24","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:24","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Ayant appris que quelques hommes partis de chez nous, et auxquels nous n\u2019avions donn\u00e9 aucun ordre, vous ont troubl\u00e9s par leurs discours et ont \u00e9branl\u00e9 vos \u00e2mes,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.25","name":"Actes 15:25","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.23","name":"Actes 15:23","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.25","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:25","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>nous avons jug\u00e9 \u00e0 propos, apr\u00e8s nous \u00eatre r\u00e9unis tous ensemble, de choisir des d\u00e9l\u00e9gu\u00e9s et de vous les envoyer avec nos bien-aim\u00e9s Barnabas et Paul,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.26","name":"Actes 15:26","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.24","name":"Actes 15:24","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.26","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:26","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>ces hommes qui ont expos\u00e9 leur vie pour le nom de notre Seigneur J\u00e9sus-Christ.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.27","name":"Actes 15:27","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.25","name":"Actes 15:25","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.27","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:27","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Nous avons donc envoy\u00e9 Jude et Silas, qui vous annonceront de leur bouche les m\u00eames choses.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.28","name":"Actes 15:28","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.26","name":"Actes 15:26","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.28","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:28","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Car il a paru bon au Saint-Esprit et \u00e0 nous de ne vous imposer d\u2019autre charge que ce qui est n\u00e9cessaire,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.29","name":"Actes 15:29","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.27","name":"Actes 15:27","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.29","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:29","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>savoir, de vous abstenir des viandes sacrifi\u00e9es aux idoles, du sang, des animaux \u00e9touff\u00e9s, et de l\u2019impudicit\u00e9, choses contre lesquelles vous vous trouverez bien de vous tenir en garde. Adieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.30","name":"Actes 15:30","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.28","name":"Actes 15:28","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.30","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:30","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.031,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 30-35: cf. \u00c9p 2:17-19. Ga 2:11-21. 1 Pi 4:10, 11.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Eux donc, ayant pris cong\u00e9 de l\u2019\u00c9glise, all\u00e8rent \u00e0 Antioche, o\u00f9 ils remirent la lettre \u00e0 la multitude assembl\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.31","name":"Actes 15:31","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.29","name":"Actes 15:29","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.31","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:31","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s l\u2019avoir lue, les fr\u00e8res furent r\u00e9jouis de l\u2019encouragement qu\u2019elle leur apportait.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.32","name":"Actes 15:32","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.30","name":"Actes 15:30","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.32","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:32","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Jude et Silas, qui \u00e9taient eux-m\u00eames proph\u00e8tes, les exhort\u00e8rent et les fortifi\u00e8rent par plusieurs discours.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.33","name":"Actes 15:33","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.31","name":"Actes 15:31","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.33","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:33","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Au bout de quelque temps, les fr\u00e8res les laiss\u00e8rent en paix retourner vers ceux qui les avaient envoy\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.34","name":"Actes 15:34","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.32","name":"Actes 15:32","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.34","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:34","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Toutefois Silas trouva bon de rester.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.35","name":"Actes 15:35","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.33","name":"Actes 15:33","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.35","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:35","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Paul et Barnabas demeur\u00e8rent \u00e0 Antioche, enseignant et annon\u00e7ant, avec plusieurs autres, la bonne nouvelle de la parole du Seigneur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.36","name":"Actes 15:36","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.34","name":"Actes 15:34","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.36","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:36","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.037,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Nouveau voyage missionnaire de Paul, accompagn\u00e9 de Silas. Visite aux \u00c9glises d\u2019Asie<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 36-41: cf. 2 Co 11:28. Ro 15:29. Ja 3:18. H\u00e9 13:18.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Quelques jours s\u2019\u00e9coul\u00e8rent, apr\u00e8s lesquels Paul dit \u00e0 Barnabas: Retournons visiter les fr\u00e8res dans toutes les villes o\u00f9 nous avons annonc\u00e9 la parole du Seigneur, pour voir en quel \u00e9tat ils sont.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.37","name":"Actes 15:37","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.35","name":"Actes 15:35","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.37","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:37","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>Barnabas voulait emmener aussi Jean, surnomm\u00e9 Marc;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.38","name":"Actes 15:38","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.36","name":"Actes 15:36","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.38","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:38","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.039,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>mais Paul jugea plus convenable de ne pas prendre avec eux celui qui les avait quitt\u00e9s depuis la Pamphylie, et qui ne les avait point accompagn\u00e9s dans leur \u0153uvre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.39","name":"Actes 15:39","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.37","name":"Actes 15:37","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.39","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:39","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.040,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup>Ce dissentiment fut assez vif pour \u00eatre cause qu\u2019ils se s\u00e9par\u00e8rent l\u2019un de l\u2019autre. Et Barnabas, prenant Marc avec lui, s\u2019embarqua pour l\u2019\u00eele de Chypre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.40","name":"Actes 15:40","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.40"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.38","name":"Actes 15:38","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"40","lastverse":"40","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.40","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.40","label":"","reference":"Actes 15:40","prev_osis_id":"Acts.015.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.015.041,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.15.40\" class=\"v\">40<\/sup>Paul fit choix de Silas, et partit, recommand\u00e9 par les fr\u00e8res \u00e0 la gr\u00e2ce du Seigneur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.15","name":"Actes 15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.15.41","name":"Actes 15:41","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.15.41"}},"previo